屋企 年輕有為有未來既 「政治犯」？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rF7knbo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrF7knbo.jpg&h=e4e36c47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMOGQ4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMOGQ4J.jpg&h=c88b19c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VfuZCKL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfuZCKL.png&h=287cbcf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放鬆夠啦<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得要長期抗爭？<br />\n<br />\n光復香港時代革命唔係一朝一夕既事<br />\n係要累積落去<br />\n<br />\n香港已經成為世界中心 對世界 國際形勢發展有所改變<br />\n我地位於鐵幕既最前線<br />\n唔好睇少自己力量 唔該 推返行動post<br />\n玩夠膠啦<br />\n玩夠屬於自己既精神國籍啦<br />\n係啦 一地都係啦 抹返先啦 遲啲先再打好冇呀？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">now or never</span></span>"},{"pid":"d60fa788d6fcaafc609233687733ae7b5cc40151","tid":1487974,"uid":206375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9Pfa54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9Pfa54.jpg&h=7e5326a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nrSHAxK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnrSHAxK.jpg&h=a1ca0400&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/COaufxK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOaufxK.jpg&h=2d6c37fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9abce0697b46671dc072901fb9d50c52976ba2a","tid":1487974,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:09:47.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"44cff6e12656c56a08a51910b2c